column5: Environment Canada has posted severe weather warnings for most of Southern Ontario, so if yer out there be careful folks! HH
Is that supposed to last all day Joe?  We didn't get anything yet.  I know Simcoe got some.  Joey
It is all over in Ontario except for the Windsor/Chatham area where it is only a WATCH.  carp-starter
All watches have been canceled now.  Too bad...I love a good storm!!

You shoulda been up here at 01:15 pm Cliff ...  We had a doozey of a storm hit...like you, I like to watch...sat on my screened-in back porch...probably have to bilge out the "Tin" before I use her...
Lots of thunder/lightening in downtown T.O right now. Just started raining hard and gusty, but no warnings yet.
